Configuration Management (Puppet, Ansible, Chef, Salt)
Configuration of Infrastructure - manage multiple servers

Puppet              Ansible
Pull                Push
Master/Slave        Agentless (Password authentication, inventory file)
                    Dynamic Inventory
Puppet language     Yaml lang to write playbooks
                    You can write your own Ansible modules by using python and can be shared
 

** Protocol for ansible to connect to windows is WIN RM
     Protocol Ansible uses to connect to Linux is SSH

** Disadvantages of Ansible
config management with windows is not as good as with Linux
Debugging
Performance
